headline: Intuit Executive Marianna Tessel to Present at the Barclays 22nd Annual Global Technology Conference
summary: MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif., December 03, 2024--Intuit Inc. (Nasdaq: INTU), the global financial technology platform that makes Intuit TurboTax, Credit Karma, QuickBooks, and Mailchimp, announced today that Marianna Tessel, executive vice president and general manager of Intuit’s Global Business Solutions Group, will present at the Barclays 22nd Annual Global Technology Conference on December 11, 2024.
